description:
L'enfant Sauvage (1970)
The Wild Child
O Garoto Selvagem

1798. In a forest, some countrymen catch a wild child who can not walk, speak, read nor write. Doctor Itard is interested by the child, and starts to educate him. Everybody thinks he will fail, but with a lot of love and patience, he manages to obtain results and the child continues with normal development. This is based on true story. http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0064285
